        "subject": "LU-5814 lov: add lov_object_xattr_get()",
        "message": "LU-5814 lov: add lov_object_xattr_get()\n\nAdd cl_object_xattr_get() to the CL object API. Implement\nlov_object_xattr_get() to return LOV xattrs for LOV objects. Add\nlov_lsm_pack() to generate LOV xattrs from a LSM.\n\nIn ll_getxattr() factor out the LOV xattr specific handling into a new\nfunction ll_getxattr_lov() which calls cl_object_xattr_get(). In\nll_listxattr() call ll_getxattr_lov() to determine if a lustre.lov\nxattr should be emitted.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I280b999381df3674e3e3693b13bf07beb5c33799\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
